title: Episode 331: Salty, Not Bitter (Feat. Sean Garrett and Ar'mon & Trey)
itunes:title: Episode 331: Salty, Not Bitter (Feat. Sean Garrett and Ar'mon & Trey)
description:
Producer, Sean Garrett and musical duo Ar'mon & Trey join the ladies of Lip Service for a wild episode! The guys add great perceptive to topics such as: being the 4th baby daddy, why men cheat vs why women cheat, and much more. Sean Garrett even opens up about the convo he had with Summer Walker regarding her song '4th Baby Mama.' Enjoy!
